# Kyverno background + admission controllers: need cluster-scoped secrets access
# to generate Kopia credentials and validate VolSync backup policies.
AVD-KSV-0041

# CloudNativePG operator: wildcard verbs on postgresql.cnpg.io are required
# for the operator to manage cluster, backup, and pooler resources.
AVD-KSV-0045

# CloudNativePG operator: must manage all CRD sub-resources for the PostgreSQL operator.
AVD-KSV-0046

# CloudNativePG operator: must create/update/delete Roles and RoleBindings
# to grant database pod service accounts access to CNPG resources.
AVD-KSV-0050

# nvidia-powerlimit DaemonSet: hostPID required for persistence-mode write
# across the driver namespace (nvidia-smi -pm 1).
AVD-KSV-0010

# nvidia-powerlimit DaemonSet: privileged required for nvidia-smi -pl;
# the driver rejects the ioctl from an unprivileged user namespace.
AVD-KSV-0017

# nvidia-powerlimit DaemonSet: consequence of privileged=true; default
# securityContext cannot be meaningfully restricted on a privileged container.
AVD-KSV-0118

# otel-agent ClusterRole: nodes/proxy access required by the kubeletstats
# receiver to scrape per-node CPU/memory metrics from the Kubelet API.
AVD-KSV-0047
